- recycling of photovoltaic panels and recovery of 98% of raw materials; 
- modular construction (dormitories, kindergartens, single- and multi-family houses, sports and military facilities, hotels, etc.);
- general contractor and architectural office;
- production and trade of militaries, robotics;
- production of military and agricultural robots;
- R&D laboratory in the industrial, agricultural and military sectors;
- advertising agency;
- humanitarian aid worldwide.

